name: Phantombuster
natural_language_description: 这是 Phantombuster 节点。主要用于: Consume Phantombuster API

resource.name: resource
resource.natural_language_description: 参数名: Resource | 默认值: agent

operation.name: operation
operation.natural_language_description: 参数名: Operation | 默认值: launch
available_options: Delete (值: delete) - Delete an agent by ID
Get (值: get) - Get an agent by ID
Get Many (值: getAll) - Get many agents of the current user's organization
Get Output (值: getOutput) - Get the output of the most recent container of an agent
Launch (值: launch) - Add an agent to the launch queue

agentId.name: agentId
agentId.description: Choose from the list, or specify an ID using an expression
agentId.natural_language_description: 参数名: Agent Name or ID | 作用: Choose from the list, or specify an ID using an expression | (必填项)

returnAll.name: returnAll
returnAll.description: Whether to return all results or only up to a given limit
returnAll.natural_language_description: 参数名: Return All | 作用: Whether to return all results or only up to a given limit | 默认值: False

limit.name: limit
limit.description: Max number of results to return
limit.natural_language_description: 参数名: Limit | 作用: Max number of results to return | 默认值: 25

resolveData.name: resolveData
resolveData.description: By default the launch just include the container ID. If this option gets activated, it will resolve the data automatically.
resolveData.natural_language_description: 参数名: Resolve Data | 作用: By default the launch just include the container ID. If this option gets activated, it will resolve the data automatically. | 默认值: True

additionalFields.name: additionalFields
additionalFields.natural_language_description: 参数名: Additional Fields | 默认值: {}
available_options: argumentsJson (值: None) - Agent argument. Can either be a JSON string or a plain object. The argument can be retrieved with buster.argument in the agent’s script.

bonusArgumentJson (值: None) - Agent bonus argument. Can either be a JSON string or a plain object. This bonus argument is single-use, it will only be used for the current launch. If present, it will be merged with the original argument, resulting in an effective argument that can be retrieved with buster.argument in the agent’s script.
manualLaunch (值: None) - Whether the agent will be considered as "launched manually"
maxInstanceCount (值: None) - If set, the agent will only be launched if the number of already running instances is below the specified number
saveArgument (值: None) - If true, argument will be saved as the default launch options for the agent

jsonParameters.name: jsonParameters
jsonParameters.natural_language_description: 参数名: JSON Parameters | 默认值: False
